title: Bobby’s Controversial Instagram Picture + Audio Of Lunchbox’s ACTUAL 911 Call + Scuba Steve Shares Unbelievable Nickname Story
itunes:title: Bobby’s Controversial Instagram Picture + Audio Of Lunchbox’s ACTUAL 911 Call + Scuba Steve Shares Unbelievable Nickname Story
description:
Bobby talks about the controversy that started last night after he posted a picture with his fiancé Caitlin. We were able to track down the 911 audio from the last time Lunchbox called the police. Plus, Scuba Steve tells us a story about his wife’s father and how it has an eerie connection to his nickname!
